        As split nears, Energizer names new board members


The Town and Country-based company's split is expected to be completed by July 1. 





















        

        
        Energizer releases new name for spinoff company: Edgewell


Once the spinoff is complete, Edgewell Personal Care will use the stock symbol EPC. 







DAVID HATFIELD
Title • CEO, Edgewell Personal CareCareer • Started at Eveready battery division in 1988. Advertising manager during Energizer Bunny launch in 1989. Promoted in 2004 to executive vice president and chief marketing officer. Named president and CEO of Schick in 2007, and later that year, president and CEO of Energizer's personal care divisionEducation • MBA from Stanford University. Bachelor's degree in economics from Princeton University




















        

        
